{
  "chapter": 45,
  "chapter_summary": "第四十六回 大惑不解。谢晓峰与燕十三在枫林中展开生死决斗。两人在对峙中互相试探，燕十三使出夺命十三剑的前十四式，谢晓峰勉强招架。关键时刻，燕十三使出第十五剑，此剑蕴含毁灭性的力量，已非人力所能控制。谢晓峰陷入必死之境，但燕十三因曾救过谢晓峰而心生犹豫，无法下手。最终燕十三选择自刎，以生命为代价毁掉这招足以毁灭天下的剑法。谢晓峰目睹燕十三之死，大惑不解。铁开诚赶到现场，谢晓峰向他解释燕十三自毁的原因——那招剑法已超越了人的控制，燕十三不愿让这样的毁灭性武学流传世间。谢晓峰深感人生矛盾，得失难分。回到客栈后，青青以暧昧姿态引路，谢晓峰在她身上看到了底层女性的悲哀与无奈。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "所以……",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 3,
      "line_end": 3
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以你只要知道我就是燕十三，也已足够了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 5,
      "line_end": 5
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "其实我只要能看到你的剑，就已足够了。",
      "tone": "轻笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 7,
      "line_end": 7
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "现在我们手里都有剑，随时都可以出手。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 31,
      "line_end": 31
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "不错。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 33,
      "line_end": 33
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "可是你一定不会轻易出手的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 35,
      "line_end": 35
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 37,
      "line_end": 37
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "因为你一定要等，等我的疏忽，等你的机会。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 39,
      "line_end": 39
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是不是也一样会等？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 41,
      "line_end": 41
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "是的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 43,
      "line_end": 43
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "只可惜这种机会绝不是很快就能等得到的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 47,
      "line_end": 47
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "所以我们一定会等很久，说不定要等到大家都已精疲力竭时，才会有这种机会出现，我相信我们一定都很沉得住气。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 51,
      "line_end": 51
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "可是我们为什么要像两个呆子一样站在这里等呢？",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 53,
      "line_end": 53
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "speaker_name": "燕十三",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你想怎么样？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 55,
      "line_end": 55
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "我们至少可以到处看看，到处去走走。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 57,
      "line_end": 57
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_yan_shi_san",
      "text": "天气这么好，风景这么美，我们在临死之前，至少也该先享受一下人生。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 59,
      "line_end": 59
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "我明白了，我明白了……",
      "tone": "喃喃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 205,
      "line_end": 205
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我却还是不明白。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 207,
      "line_end": 207
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "是你？你也来了！",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 215,
      "line_end": 215
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "是我，我早就来了，可是我一直都不明白！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 217,
      "line_end": 217
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你应该知道我一直都希望也能再见他一面。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 219,
      "line_end": 219
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "我知道，我当然知道！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 221,
      "line_end": 221
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "他一定也很想再见你，因为你虽然不是他的子弟，却是他剑法惟一的传人，他一定希望你能看到他最后那一剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 235,
      "line_end": 235
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那一剑就是他剑法中的精粹？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 237,
      "line_end": 237
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "不错，那就是‘夺命十三剑’中的第十五种变化，普天之下，绝没有任何人能招架闪避。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 239,
      "line_end": 239
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你也不能？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 241,
      "line_end": 241
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "我也不能。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 243,
      "line_end": 243
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是他并没有用那一剑杀了你。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 245,
      "line_end": 245
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "那一剑若是真的击出，我已必死无疑，只可惜到了最后一瞬问，他那一剑竟无法刺出来！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 247,
      "line_end": 247
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 249,
      "line_end": 249
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "因为他心里没有杀机！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 251,
      "line_end": 251
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "为什么？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 255,
      "line_end": 255
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "因为他救过我的命！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 257,
      "line_end": 257
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "如果你救过一个人的命，就很难再下手杀他，因为你跟这个人已经有了感情。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 261,
      "line_end": 261
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "就算他不忍下手杀你，也不必死的！",
      "tone": "激动",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 267,
      "line_end": 267
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "本来我也想不通他为什么要死！",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 269,
      "line_end": 269
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "现在你已想通了？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 271,
      "line_end": 271
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "现在我才明白，他实在非死不可。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 273,
      "line_end": 273
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "因为在那一瞬间，他心里虽然不想杀我，不忍杀我，却已无法控制他手里的剑，因为那一剑的力量，本就不是任何人能控制的，只要一发出来，就一定要有人死在剑下。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 277,
      "line_end": 277
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我还是不明白他为什么一定要毁了自己。",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 283,
      "line_end": 283
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "他想毁的，并不是他自己，而是那一剑。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 285,
      "line_end": 285
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那一剑既然是登峰造极，天下无双的剑法，他为什么要毁了它？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 287,
      "line_end": 287
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "因为他忽然发现，那一剑所带来的只有毁灭和死亡，他绝不能让这样的剑法留传世上，他不愿做武学中的罪人。",
      "tone": "严肃",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 289,
      "line_end": 289
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "所以他只有自己先毁了自己。",
      "tone": "恐惧",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 293,
      "line_end": 293
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "因为他的生命骨肉，都已经和这条毒龙融为一体，因为这条毒龙本来就是他这个人的精粹，所以他要消灭这条毒龙，就一定要先把自己毁灭。",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 295,
      "line_end": 295
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "可是在那一瞬间，他的确已到达剑法中前无古人，后无来者的巅峰，他已死而无憾了。",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 303,
      "line_end": 303
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你是不是宁愿死的是你自己？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 305,
      "line_end": 305
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "是的！",
      "tone": "悲伤",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 307,
      "line_end": 307
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你回来了？",
      "tone": "暧昧",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 337,
      "line_end": 337
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "后面还有人在等你，已经等了很久！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 345,
      "line_end": 345
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 347,
      "line_end": 347
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "“他们人在哪里？”",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 351,
      "line_end": 351
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我带你去。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 353,
      "line_end": 353
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "这里没有人等你。",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 361,
      "line_end": 361
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我知道！",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 363,
      "line_end": 363
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "我也没有叫你跟着来！",
      "tone": "淡然",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 365,
      "line_end": 365
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "speaker_name": "铁开诚",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你没有。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 367,
      "line_end": 367
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_tie_kai_cheng",
      "text": "那么你为什么不到前面去等？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 369,
      "line_end": 369
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "前天晚上，我本来准备去找你的。",
      "tone": "暧昧",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 373,
      "line_end": 373
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "哦？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 375,
      "line_end": 375
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "我连脚都洗过了。",
      "tone": "暧昧",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 377,
