    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "因为我知道那个女人给我的钱，一定比你给我的多，我看得出你绝不是个肯在女人身上花钱的男人。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 383,
      "line_end": 383
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "可是只要你喜欢，今天晚上我还是可以……",
      "tone": "暧昧",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 385,
      "line_end": 385
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "我若不喜欢呢？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 387,
      "line_end": 387
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "那么我就去找你那个朋友，我看得出他一定会喜欢的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 389,
      "line_end": 389
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
      "listener": "char_qing_qing",
      "text": "你应该去！",
      "tone": "认真",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 401,
      "line_end": 401
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_qing_qing",
      "speaker_name": "青青",
      "listener": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "text": "你会不会觉得我是个很不要脸的女人？",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 45,
      "line_start": 413,
      "line_end": 413
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_xie_xiao_feng",
      "speaker_name": "谢晓峰",
